vernac_cmds: Inductive form : Set := | Falsum : form | Atom : Int -> form | AndF : form -> form -> form | OrF : form -> form -> form | Imp : form -> form -> form.
Fixpoint vimp (qs : list Int) : form -> form := match qs with | nil => fun a : form => a | q :: qs => fun a : form => vimp qs (Imp (Atom q) a) end.

Fixpoint subst_form (i : Int) (a b : form) {struct b} : form := match b with | Falsum => Falsum | Atom j => match equal_dec i j with | left _ => a | right _ => Atom j end | OrF b0 b1 => OrF (subst_form i a b0) (subst_form i a b1) | AndF b0 b1 => AndF (subst_form i a b0) (subst_form i a b1) | Imp b0 b1 => Imp (subst_form i a b0) (subst_form i a b1) end.
Definition subst_list (i : Int) (a : form) (l : flist) := map (subst_form i a) l.
Lemma subst_nth : forall (i : Int) (g : form) (n : nat) (l : flist) (a : form), my_nth form n l a -> my_nth form n (subst_list i g l) (subst_form i g a).
intros i g n; elim n; clear n.
intros l a nth; inversion_clear nth.
intros n ih l a nth.

Fixpoint below_form (a : form) (i : Int) {struct a} : Prop := match a with | Falsum => True | Atom j => Less j i | AndF a0 a1 => below_form a0 i /\ below_form a1 i | OrF a0 a1 => below_form a0 i /\ below_form a1 i | Imp a0 a1 => below_form a0 i /\ below_form a1 i end.
Definition below_list (L : flist) (i : Int) := forall a : form, In a L -> below_form a i.
Lemma below_form_less_below_form : forall (a : form) (i j : Int), below_form a i -> Less i j -> below_form a j.
intros a ih_a b ih_b below_ab less_ij.
intros a ih_a b ih_b below_ab less_ij.
intros a ih_a b ih_b below_ab less_ij.
Lemma below_list_less_below_list : forall (l : flist) (i j : Int), below_list l i -> Less i j -> below_list l j.
intros l i j below_l less_ij.
Lemma below_cons_list_head : forall (a : form) (l : flist) (i : Int), below_list (a :: l) i -> below_form a i.
Lemma below_cons_list_tail : forall (a : form) (l : flist) (i : Int), below_list (a :: l) i -> below_list l i.
Lemma below_cons_list : forall (a : form) (l : flist) (i : Int), below_form a i -> below_list l i -> below_list (a :: l) i.
intros a l i below_a below_l.
Lemma below_list_weak : forall (l : flist) (a b : form) (i : Int), (below_form a i -> below_form b i) -> below_list (a :: l) i -> below_list (b :: l) i.
intros l a b i below_ab below_l.
Lemma below_list_weak2 : forall (l : flist) (a b c : form) (i : Int), (below_form a i -> below_form b i /\ below_form c i) -> below_list (a :: l) i -> below_list (b :: c :: l) i.
intros l a b c i below_abc below_l.
Lemma subst_form_below : forall (i : Int) (g a : form), below_form a i -> subst_form i g a = a.
intros i g a; elim a; clear a.
intros a ih_a b ih_b below_ab.
intros a ih_a b ih_b below_ab.
intros a ih_a b ih_b below_ab.
Lemma subst_list_below : forall (i : Int) (g : form) (l : flist), below_list l i -> subst_list i g l = l.
intros i g l; elim l; clear l.
simpl in |- *; intros a l ih below_l.
Lemma below_vimp : forall (j : Int) (l : list Int) (a b : form), (forall j : Int, below_form a j -> below_form b j) -> below_form (vimp l a) j -> below_form (vimp l b) j.
simpl in |- *; intros i l ih a b below_ab below_a.
apply ih with (a := Imp (Atom i) a); try assumption.
elim below_ia; clear below_ia; intros below_i below_a0.

Lemma below_vimp2 : forall (j : Int) (l : list Int) (a b c : form), (forall j : Int, below_form a j -> below_form b j -> below_form c j) -> below_form (vimp l a) j -> below_form (vimp l b) j -> below_form (vimp l c) j.
intros a b c below_abc below_a below_b.
simpl in |- *; intros i l ih a b c below_abc below_a below_b.
apply ih with (a := Imp (Atom i) a) (b := Imp (Atom i) b); try assumption.
elim below_ia; clear below_ia; intros below_i below_a0.
elim below_ib; clear below_ib; intros below_i0 below_b0.
Lemma below_vimp_head : forall (j : Int) (l : list Int) (a : form), below_form (vimp l a) j -> below_form a j.
intros j l; elim l; clear l.
intros i l ih a below_la.
Lemma below_vimp_split : forall (j : Int) (l : list Int) (a : form), (forall i : Int, In i l -> Less i j) -> below_form a j -> below_form (vimp l a) j.
intros j l; elim l; clear l.
intros i l ih a below_i below_a.
apply ih with (a := Imp (Atom i) a).
Lemma below_vimp_tail : forall (j : Int) (l : list Int) (a : form), below_form (vimp l a) j -> forall i : Int, In i l -> Less i j.
intros j l; elim l; clear l.
intros a below_la i0 in0; inversion_clear in0.
simpl in |- *; intros i l ih a below_la i0 in0.
elim (below_vimp_head j l (Imp (Atom i) a) below_la).
apply ih with (a := Imp (Atom i) a); assumption.
Lemma subst_vimp_head : forall (j : Int) (a : form) (l : list Int) (b : form), (forall i : Int, In i l -> Less i j) -> subst_form j a (vimp l b) = vimp l (subst_form j a b).
intros j a l; elim l; clear l.
intros i l ih b below_l.
change (vimp l (Imp (subst_form j a (Atom i)) (subst_form j a b)) = vimp l (Imp (Atom i) (subst_form j a b))) in |- *.
Lemma max_int_of_form : forall a : form, {j : Int | below_form a j}.
intros a; elim a; clear a.
intros i; elim (int_succ i); intros i1 less1.
Lemma max_int_of_list : forall Gamma : flist, {j : Int | below_list Gamma j}.
intros Gamma; elim Gamma; clear Gamma.
unfold below_list in |- *; intros a in_a; inversion_clear in_a.
